00:01:24.940 --> 00:01:28.160
[Whispers of Fate]

00:01:28.330 --> 00:01:29.930
[Episode 20]

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:31.910
You want the rights of the Sword Alliance

00:01:31.910 --> 00:01:33.910
yet refuse to abide by its rules.

00:01:34.070 --> 00:01:35.840
That's something we cannot agree to.

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.710
Are you two implying

00:01:38.039 --> 00:01:38.950
that either

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:40.200
I am

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:42.950
unworthy of serving
as the Alliance's Guest of Honor

00:01:42.950 --> 00:01:43.710
or that

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:46.420
the Sword Alliance itself

00:01:46.590 --> 00:01:49.050
is unworthy of having
a Guest of Honor at all?

00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:54.950
Ever since Mr. Tang entered the jianghu,

00:01:54.950 --> 00:01:55.710
his every deed

00:01:55.710 --> 00:01:56.990
has proven his worth—

00:01:57.020 --> 00:01:57.990
skilled in martial arts

00:01:57.990 --> 00:01:59.190
and unmatched in wit.

00:01:59.509 --> 00:02:00.840
If we reject him now,

00:02:01.230 --> 00:02:02.000
it would make us seem

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.000
narrow-minded,

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:05.300
unable to tolerate a rising talent.

00:02:05.350 --> 00:02:06.510
But Mr. Tang,
you've always ignored the rules

00:02:06.510 --> 00:02:08.240
and gone wherever you pleased.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:10.229
You now suddenly wish
to join the Sword Alliance,

00:02:10.229 --> 00:02:12.150
claiming to serve
for the peace in the jianghu.

00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:13.880
Doesn't that seem suspicious?

00:02:15.630 --> 00:02:17.230
If I were to join the Alliance

00:02:17.470 --> 00:02:19.000
with no desire or ambition,

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:21.570
willingly serving beneath others,

00:02:21.570 --> 00:02:23.370
wouldn't that be even stranger?

00:02:23.910 --> 00:02:26.000
Since I wish
to serve as the Guest of Honor,

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.030
you sword masters should

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:28.470
feel reassured instead.

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:30.280
Doesn't that precisely show

00:02:30.620 --> 00:02:31.550
that I am willing

00:02:31.930 --> 00:02:33.329
to take on responsibility

00:02:33.329 --> 00:02:34.660
for the Sword Alliance?

00:02:35.980 --> 00:02:37.690
The Fengliu Shop has already thrown
the jianghu into chaos.

00:02:37.690 --> 00:02:38.750
Now more than ever,

00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:40.460
the Sword Alliance
must not fall into disorder.

00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:41.470
We cannot accept

00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:43.250
an uncontrollable and dangerous man.

00:02:43.250 --> 00:02:44.090
So,

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:47.110
what you guys mean is,

00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:48.990
the current Sword Alliance

00:02:49.030 --> 00:02:51.030
doesn't need any change

00:02:51.190 --> 00:02:53.120
to stand against the Fengliu Shop?

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.040
Is that right?

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.360
I understand now.

00:02:57.540 --> 00:02:58.770
In their understanding,

00:02:58.770 --> 00:02:59.560
the greater the power,

00:02:59.560 --> 00:03:00.890
the greater the danger.

00:03:01.220 --> 00:03:02.220
I believe

00:03:02.490 --> 00:03:03.610
everyone here

00:03:04.030 --> 00:03:05.190
has the resolve to fight

00:03:05.190 --> 00:03:06.850
the Fengliu Shop to the death.

00:03:08.250 --> 00:03:10.110
But if resolve alone were enough,

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:12.000
would the Sword Alliance

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:13.630
still be so disorganized?

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:16.520
If all of you could win

00:03:16.550 --> 00:03:17.950
by risking your lives,

00:03:17.970 --> 00:03:18.900
then Master Shao

00:03:18.940 --> 00:03:19.720
wouldn't have

00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:21.720
let me, Tang Lici, stand here today.

00:03:21.720 --> 00:03:22.920
What did you just say?

00:03:27.100 --> 00:03:29.329
The Fengliu Shop isn't a gang
of petty thieves,

00:03:29.329 --> 00:03:30.590
nor mountain bandits.

00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:31.750
They have not only

00:03:31.750 --> 00:03:33.740
the ambition
to plunge the world into chaos

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:35.810
but also endless cunning schemes.

00:03:36.130 --> 00:03:39.320
The enemy is advancing fiercely—
but the Sword Alliance?

00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:42.180
Still clinging to old rules
and refusing to change.

00:03:42.370 --> 00:03:44.370
Isn't that asking for destruction?

00:03:44.870 --> 00:03:45.430
Mr. Tang,

00:03:45.550 --> 00:03:46.530
that's nonsense!

00:03:46.530 --> 00:03:47.340
Master Xiao,

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.120
what the Alliance needs now

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:49.490
is not caution,

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:50.670
but change.

00:03:50.690 --> 00:03:51.890
Only if I join

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:54.020
will there be a sliver of hope.

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.870
If you don't even have the courage

00:03:55.870 --> 00:03:57.000
to accept me,

00:03:57.060 --> 00:03:58.260
how could you speak of

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:00.930
having the courage
to fight the Fengliu Shop?

00:04:00.930 --> 00:04:02.590
Since you are courting death,

00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:03.910
what difference is there

00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:05.110
between dying sooner

00:04:05.500 --> 00:04:06.820
and dying later?

00:04:07.390 --> 00:04:08.150
Stop talking nonsense.

00:04:08.150 --> 00:04:08.810
Or perhaps—

00:04:09.310 --> 00:04:10.150
you fear me…

00:04:12.670 --> 00:04:14.130
more than you fear Liu Yan?

00:04:14.590 --> 00:04:15.590
We don't fear you!

00:04:16.430 --> 00:04:17.630
Everyone, calm down.

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.430
Mr. Tang truly is

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:25.200
sharp-witted and quick-tongued.

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:26.240
The six of us

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:28.080
cannot out-argue you alone.

00:04:28.290 --> 00:04:29.170
However,

00:04:30.860 --> 00:04:33.340
your appointment
as the Guest of Honor

00:04:33.530 --> 00:04:35.330
is a matter of great importance.

00:04:35.490 --> 00:04:37.380
According to the Sword Alliance's rules
of procedure,

00:04:37.380 --> 00:04:38.150
the six of us initiated a vote.

00:04:38.150 --> 00:04:39.670
[Tang Lici's appointment
as the Guest of Honor]

00:04:39.670 --> 00:04:40.000
[requires the Ancestor's approval,
or it cannot proceed.]

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.040
So today,

00:04:41.130 --> 00:04:42.990
we're not here to debate with you—

00:04:43.270 --> 00:04:45.070
just to inform you of the result.

00:04:49.820 --> 00:04:50.950
What does that mean?

00:04:51.590 --> 00:04:52.710
It means

00:04:53.340 --> 00:04:55.140
with this voting result in hand,

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:58.310
Master Shao's decision no longer counts.

00:04:59.070 --> 00:05:00.070
Unless

00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:01.240
you can somehow overturn

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.430
the rules laid down

00:05:02.860 --> 00:05:03.790
by the Ancestor.

00:05:05.190 --> 00:05:06.980
They call themselves righteous,

00:05:06.980 --> 00:05:08.660
yet they're so shameless.

00:05:09.190 --> 00:05:10.120
But that's fine,

00:05:10.230 --> 00:05:11.360
not a problem at all.

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:12.790
Foxy Tang,

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.100
if this place won't have you,

00:05:14.100 --> 00:05:16.390
you can always
find somewhere else that will.

00:05:16.390 --> 00:05:16.920
Let's go.

00:05:17.230 --> 00:05:18.030
Wait a moment.

00:05:34.970 --> 00:05:35.770
Master Puzhu.

00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:36.950
You came to…

00:05:41.350 --> 00:05:43.400
I heard Mr. Tang arrived
at the Sword Alliance,

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:44.659
so I came immediately.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:46.310
Master Puzhu,

00:05:46.330 --> 00:05:48.140
are you here
to have me honor our agreement now?

00:05:48.140 --> 00:05:49.500
You once promised me

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.450
that once you reached the Sword Alliance,

00:05:51.450 --> 00:05:52.450
you'd fight me

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:53.720
in Qingyang Realm.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.070
No time

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:56.720
like the present.

00:06:04.670 --> 00:06:05.920
Before we begin,

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.530
I'd like to know,

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:08.910
Master Puzhu, whether you too

00:06:08.910 --> 00:06:10.170
are unwilling to see me

00:06:10.450 --> 00:06:12.180
take the seat of Guest of Honor?

00:06:12.190 --> 00:06:13.680
You do things without regard

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.610
for convention.

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:18.970
Forgive me, but I cannot condone that.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:21.950
It seems

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.200
you've misunderstood me.

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:27.140
A misunderstanding

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:28.400
should be cleared up.

00:06:28.620 --> 00:06:30.150
We'll talk after the fight.

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:34.720
Everyone,

00:06:35.110 --> 00:06:36.510
once the duel is decided,

00:06:36.620 --> 00:06:38.820
I'll personally see Mr. Tang off.

00:06:39.450 --> 00:06:40.040
Then,

00:06:40.810 --> 00:06:42.720
I won't disturb your meeting any further.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:43.250
Let's go.

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:52.070
Mr. Tang and Master Puzhu

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.430
are dueling in Qingyang Realm!

00:06:53.430 --> 00:06:54.690
Hurry, let's go watch!

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:56.360
Is it really that fox spirit,

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:57.159
Mr. Tang Lici?

00:06:57.390 --> 00:06:58.960
Is he really as powerful
as the rumors say?

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.070
Go see for yourself!

00:07:00.070 --> 00:07:00.600
Let's go!

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:09.970
[The Peak of Heaven]

00:07:13.100 --> 00:07:14.530
[Qingyang Realm]

00:07:19.870 --> 00:07:21.440
Why fight in Qingyang Realm?

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.540
Is there some special reason?

00:07:22.540 --> 00:07:24.080
Probably to make it seem more formal.

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:25.720
Long ago, Ancestor Zhao Quanyang

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:27.760
held the Central Plains
Martial Arts Tournament here,

00:07:27.760 --> 00:07:29.090
creating six divine swords

00:07:29.090 --> 00:07:31.160
and entrusting them
to six masters of their era.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:33.030
That was the origin of the Sword Alliance.

00:07:33.030 --> 00:07:35.020
It's said that when the Ancestor ascended
in broad daylight,

00:07:35.020 --> 00:07:36.810
his sword energy filled heaven and earth,

00:07:36.810 --> 00:07:38.500
summoning a golden dragon from the skies.

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.560
Then he rode the dragon and ascended.

00:07:41.190 --> 00:07:42.190
Stop right there.

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:44.730
We take those tales as stories.

00:07:44.830 --> 00:07:45.770
You actually believe them?

00:07:45.770 --> 00:07:46.630
Of course we do.

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:48.830
Every disciple of the Sword Alliance

00:07:48.830 --> 00:07:50.430
honors the Ancestor deeply.

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:53.510
Mr. Tang,

00:07:54.630 --> 00:07:55.120
please.

00:08:04.540 --> 00:08:05.540
