00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:29.930
♪ The endless seas and lands ♪

00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:35.320
♪ Await my burning passion ♪

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:43.570
♪ Facing swords and blades, I roar alone ♪

00:09:44.210 --> 00:09:49.790
♪ With supreme power,
