00:09:51.350 --> 00:09:52.120
the sword energy left behind

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:53.120
when the Ancestor transcended

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:54.000
the Broken Void Realm.

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:56.790
♪ A roar, and winds and clouds howl ♪

00:09:56.820 --> 00:09:59.020
♪ Behold the land, miles wide ♪

00:09:59.090 --> 00:10:02.250
