♪ I've come, yet you're not here ♪

00:39:26.790 --> 00:39:29.260
♪ Only wind and rain ♪

00:39:30.220 --> 00:39:33.860
♪ Mountain path ends,
and soft wind blows ♪

00:39:33.880 --> 00:39:35.290
♪ Clouds gone, night quiet,
birds sing alone ♪

00:39:35.290 --> 00:39:36.220
Don't be afraid.

00:39:36.360 --> 00:39:36.860
This is Zhoudi Tower.

00:39:36.860 --> 00:39:39.400
♪ On the endless cold night ♪

00:39:39.590 --> 00:39:39.740
From now on,

00:39:39.740 --> 00:39:40.710
♪ Strange is but the crescent moon ♪

00:39:40.710 --> 00:39:42.370
no one will force you anymore.

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:43.490
Believe in yourself.

00:39:43.490 --> 00:39:44.110
♪ The flute fades far away ♪

00:39:44.110 --> 00:39:45.110
You won't hurt it.

