♪ What's familiar will also change ♪

00:39:50.340 --> 00:39:53.070
♪ Ice melts in palms ♪

00:39:53.250 --> 00:39:54.960
♪ Hands warm a soul ♪

00:39:54.960 --> 00:39:55.730
Touch it.

00:39:56.810 --> 00:39:58.830
♪ Dream of you once,
and miss you 10,000 times ♪

00:39:59.140 --> 00:40:01.800
♪ Spring sounds break,
and dreams never wake ♪

00:40:01.800 --> 00:40:02.510
See?

00:40:03.110 --> 00:40:03.900
It actually likes you.

00:40:03.900 --> 00:40:06.730
♪ Echoes sink in silent surges ♪

00:40:06.760 --> 00:40:10.230
♪ Surpassing many words ♪

00:40:10.810 --> 00:40:13.540
♪ On the way back, a half-lit oil lamp ♪

00:40:13.560 --> 00:40:14.170
♪ Wet ink stains surge and overflow ♪

00:40:14.170 --> 00:40:15.080
"Human nature"

00:40:15.870 --> 00:40:16.990
"is originally good."

00:40:16.990 --> 00:40:23.390
♪ Hope what's hopeful,
and let go of anger in a day ♪

00:40:23.750 --> 00:40:27.150
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
live up to it, and never let you go ♪

00:40:27.150 --> 00:40:27.950
It seems that…

00:40:29.870 --> 00:40:31.670
you, like the old me,

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:33.670
need someone patient

00:40:33.670 --> 00:40:35.110
to teach you.

00:40:40.360 --> 00:40:41.920
Where did Liu Yan go?

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:43.230
Tang Lici

00:40:43.590 --> 00:40:45.390
must have said something to him.

00:40:45.820 --> 00:40:46.530
Otherwise,

00:40:46.780 --> 00:40:48.240
as long as Liu Yan is alive,

00:40:48.670 --> 00:40:51.220
he would've returned
to Xiuyu Peony Pavilion.

00:40:51.220 --> 00:40:52.380
He didn't come back.

00:40:53.120 --> 00:40:54.890
He must have gone to a place

00:40:54.910 --> 00:40:56.310
that matters more to him.

00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:35.590
How are you? Are you all right?

00:41:53.270 --> 00:41:54.070
[Zhoudi Tower]

00:41:54.070 --> 00:41:55.730
I understand your situation.

00:41:56.320 --> 00:41:57.710
Then from today onward,

00:41:57.920 --> 00:41:59.330
I'm your brother.

00:41:59.740 --> 00:42:00.410
This place

00:42:01.360 --> 00:42:02.630
is your home.

00:42:03.030 --> 00:42:03.800
Let's go.

00:42:16.950 --> 00:42:17.950
"Human nature…"

00:42:18.440 --> 00:42:19.440
"Human nature…"

00:42:19.800 --> 00:42:21.060
"Is originally good."

00:42:21.230 --> 00:42:22.490
"Is originally good."

00:42:22.590 --> 00:42:24.520
"Human nature is originally good"

00:42:24.620 --> 00:42:25.510
means

00:42:26.000 --> 00:42:27.600
when we come into this world,

00:42:27.830 --> 00:42:30.020
we are inherently kind.

00:42:31.310 --> 00:42:32.310
Am I, too?

00:42:35.150 --> 00:42:36.150
Of course.

00:42:36.670 --> 00:42:37.670
Yan,

00:42:37.850 --> 00:42:39.310
you're the kindest of all.

00:42:48.230 --> 00:42:49.290
What are you doing?

00:42:49.970 --> 00:42:50.560
Give it back.

00:42:50.560 --> 00:42:51.660
Why are you chasing me?

00:42:51.660 --> 00:42:53.140
Xianling Herb is for making soup,

00:42:53.140 --> 00:42:54.260
not for feeding curse bugs.

00:42:54.260 --> 00:42:55.990
Let me feed it to the bugs first.

00:42:56.580 --> 00:42:57.400
Give it back to me.

00:42:57.400 --> 00:42:57.960
Don't chase me!

00:42:57.960 --> 00:42:58.630
If you want it,

00:42:58.630 --> 00:42:59.890
go pick some yourself.

00:43:04.230 --> 00:43:04.800
Come back.

00:43:04.800 --> 00:43:05.880
Don't chase me.

00:43:38.650 --> 00:43:40.450
It's Fang Zhou's heart crystal.

00:43:40.960 --> 00:43:42.000
He's still alive.

00:43:45.080 --> 00:43:46.290
Fang Zhou's corpse

00:43:46.640 --> 00:43:48.260
is still in Zhoudi Tower.

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:50.280
I used Biluo Palace's

00:43:50.280 --> 00:43:52.540
Immortal Crystal Coffin to preserve it.

00:43:54.430 --> 00:43:55.550
Tang Lici,

00:43:56.170 --> 00:43:58.370
I've decided to trust you one more time.

00:44:00.460 --> 00:44:01.540
Hidden-wing Bug.

